name: DarkFab
css:
@-moz-document domain("sketchfab.com") {
.c-page-header,
.c-page-header .c-user-menu__avatar .image-container,
.viewer.transparent-pattern,
.collection-smallcard, .model-smallcard,
.card,
.activity,
.c-page-header .c-user-menu .hover-menu,
.categories-navigation,
.hover-menu,
.settings>.inner,
.popup-container .popup .popup-header,
.popup-container .popup .popup-footer,
.c-page-header__action__popin,
.c-popup,
.two-columns.sidebar-right .right .sidebar-box,
.model-management__header
{
    background: #222;
}

.header-content,
.popup-container .popup,
.header-content .header-menu .elements .item,
.c-card-slider__background
{
    background: #2f2f2f;
}

.card-collection {
    box-shadow: 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,.2), 0 6px 0 -3px #111, 0 6px 1px -3px rgba(0,0,0,.2), 0 12px 0 -6px #222, 0 12px 2px -6px rgba(0,0,0,.2), 0 7px 18px 0 rgba(97,108,121,.13);
}

body,
body.white-background,
.form-content>:first-child,
.form-select select,
.form-select:after,
.two-columns.model-container,
.content-white,.home .latest-news

{
    background: #333;
}

.header-content.container,
.model-container .main .model-informations{
    background: none;
}

h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, .h1, .h2, .h3, .h4, .h5, .h6,
.collection-smallcard .meta .information .name, .model-smallcard .meta .information .name,
.model-smallcard .meta .information .name .model-name__label,
.c-page-header__action__icon,
.c-page-header .c-navigation__item,
.user-name__link .text,
.model-container .main .model-informations .description-content,
.c-model-comments__title,
.c-model-comments .comment-item__text p,
.model-container .main .viewer-additional h1.model-name .model-name__label,
.card__footer__title a.model-name__label,
.card__footer__title,
.activity__title,
.activity-filters__item input[type=radio]:checked+label,
.hover-menu, .model-license__name,
.categories-navigation .navigation-item a, .community-navigation .navigation-item a,
.sidebar .link,
.page-title,
.form-label,
.settings .settings-name,
.more,
p,
.subtitle,
.form-content>:first-child,
.form-select select,
.settings h4,
.settings .notifications .label,
.settings .notifications .notification-option .description,
.settings__social-connect-label,
.settings-account .section,
.popup-title,
.popup-container .popup .popup-content,
.main-footer,
.model-management__status, .model-container .main .model-informations__stats,.model-container .main .model-informations__list
{
    color:#ddd !important;
}

.c-page-header__action__popin:after{
    color: #222;
}

.c-page-header,
.categories-navigation .highlights-list,
.c-page-header.\--scroll,
.model-container .main .model-informations,
.c-card-slider__background,
.form-content>:first-child,
.form-select select,
.form-select:after,
.header-content,
.hover-menu .separator:not(:first-child), .hover-menu .viewer .controls .control .control-menu li.hr:not(:first-child), .viewer .controls .control .control-menu .hover-menu li.hr:not(:first-child),
.two-columns.sidebar-right .right .sidebar-box,.model-management__section:not(:first-child)
{
    border: none;
    box-shadow: none;
}

.categories-navigation,
.c-page-header .c-user-menu__avatar .image-container{
    border-radius: 0;
}
}
